def transform_dataset(test_list):
    result = []
    temp = []
    
    for item in test_list:
        if item == ['']:
            result.append(temp)
            temp = []
        else:
            temp.extend(item)
    
    if temp:  # Capture any remaining items after the last delimiter
        result.append(temp)
        
    return result
